### TABLEDATA

CREATE TABLE tissue_data (
    tissue_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    tissue_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    gene_id INT NOT NULL,
    expression_level FLOAT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE conditions_data (
    condition_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    condition_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    gene_id INT NOT NULL,
    expression_level FLOAT NOT NULL
);

### STATEMENT

UPDATE tissue_data SET expression_level = 0.5 WHERE gene_id = 100
